Package: VGheatmap
Type: Package
Title: Creates Heat Map Graphics for Insurgency (Source Engine FPS)
Version: 0.0.05
Author: Kenneth Buker
Maintainer: <KCIV4@att.net>
Description: Asks for an import of coordinate data, and will display this data in a heatmap against map images from Insurgency using GGplot2. The theme and format are tailored for 1024x1024 background image, but this can be changed if needed.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Depends: jpeg,ggplot2,cowplot, R (>= 2.10)
Imports: grid,jpeg,ggplot2,cowplot
